OL,6,FDrastic spending cuts in the
OL,7,Fhealthcare service would still leave a
OL,8,F#189 million budget deficit, Robin
OL,9,FSwann has warned.
OL,11,FThe Health Minister has told Executive
OL,12,Fministers and members of the health
OL,13,Fcommittee that "deep dive" cuts to
OL,14,Fhealth spending would not avoid a
OL,15,Fmultimillion-pound overspend in the
OL,16,Fdepartment.
