OL,6,FMr Swann wrote to his fellow Executive
OL,7,Fministers: "The assessment details
OL,8,Fthat even after extensive deep dive
OL,9,Fsavings measures, a remaining deficit
OL,10,Fof #189m is anticipated.
OL,12,F"That estimated deficit is in addition
OL,13,Fto the fact that no funding is
OL,14,Fprovided in the Executive's budget for
OL,15,Fstaff pay increases, meaning further
OL,16,Findustrial action is all but
OL,17,Finevitable in the year ahead."
