OL,6,FIt said that all trusts had expressed
OL,7,F"grave concerns" about the impact on
OL,8,Fhealth and social care services at
OL,9,Fboth local and regional level if such
OL,10,Fsavings measures were to be requested.
OL,12,FSome of the "projected" requirements
OL,13,Finclude a reduction of around 400
OL,14,Facute hospital beds across Northern
OL,15,FIreland, a reduction of around 1,200
OL,16,Fstaff; an estimated reduction of
OL,17,F1,100,000 hours of homecare/
OL,18,Fdomiciliary care type support over a
OL,19,Fyear; and an estimated reduction of
OL,20,Faround 500 care home beds.
